    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extensible Markup Language, or XML, is a markup language and file format for storing, transmitting, and reconstructing arbitrary data. Based on SGML, it allows the mark-up of electronic documents, and can aid the exchange of data via the World Wide Web, and allows users to customize tags.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
